name: Flamboyant /ˈneɪtʃə/
description: "Climb the peaks to hear the good news. As the light shines on the trees, the calm of nature will behear you. The winds will bring their own freshness to you, and the storms will bring their own vigor, while your worries will fall away like Autumn leaves. Enjoy the nature while it's there." By @Baimtje
